<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="65" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,1482,1687]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,1482,1507]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, T. H." box="[281,454,1482,1507]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" pagination="856 - 915" refId="ref14825" refString="Perkins, T. H. (1985) Chrysopetalum, Bhawania and two new genera of Chrysopetalidae (Polychaeta) from Florida. Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington, 98, 856 - 915." type="journal article" year="1985">Perkins (1985)</bibRefCitation>
redefined the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schmarda" authorityYear="1861" box="[716,829,1483,1507]" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Bhawania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[716,829,1483,1507]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Bhawania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with a complete description of the body and the morphological characters of the segments, but he did not emphasize the importance of the paleae morphology. He also suggested that the species composition of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schmarda" authorityYear="1861" box="[704,818,1555,1579]" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Bhawania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[704,818,1555,1579]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Bhawania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
needs to be reassesed and requires a major revision especially with regards to the paleae. This need is reflected in some species originally described as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schmarda" authorityYear="1861" box="[1272,1385,1590,1614]" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Bhawania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1272,1385,1590,1614]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Bhawania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but subsequently reassigned to other genera, as 
<taxonomicName authority="(Gallardo, 1968)" authorityName="Gallardo" authorityYear="1968" baseAuthorityName="Gallardo" baseAuthorityYear="1968" box="[647,1048,1626,1651]" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Paleaequor" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="brevis">
<emphasis box="[647,853,1627,1651]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Paleaequor brevis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Gallardo, V. A." box="[869,1040,1626,1651]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" pagination="35 - 279" refId="ref13562" refString="Gallardo, V. A. (1968) Polychaeta from the Bay of Nha Trang, South Vietnam. Naga report, 4 (3), 35 - 279." type="journal article" year="1968">Gallardo, 1968</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="(Katzmann, Laubier &amp; Ramos, 1974)" authorityName="Katzmann, Laubier &amp; Ramos" authorityYear="1974" baseAuthorityName="Katzmann, Laubier &amp; Ramos" baseAuthorityYear="1974" class="Polychaeta" family="Chrysopetalidae" genus="Arichlidon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="reyssi">
<emphasis box="[1105,1296,1627,1651]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Arichlidon reyssi</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Katzmann, W. &amp; Laubier, L. &amp; Ramos, J." pageId="4" pageNumber="65" pagination="313 - 317" refId="ref14197" refString="Katzmann, W., Laubier, L. &amp; Ramos, J. (1974) Une nouvelle espece Mediterraneene de Chrysopetalidae (Annelides Polychetes). Annalen des Naturhistorischen Museums in Wien, 78, 313 - 317." type="journal article" year="1974">Katzmann, Laubier &amp; Ramos, 1974</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
